metadata.title: Seabirds and Marine Mammal Counts in PWS

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest, Cordova Ranger District

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds/Mammals; Seabird and marine mammal counts along 60 randomly selected 0.8 km transects from shoreline out 5 km around Naked, Storey, and Peak Islands. Survey dates 1991: 7-9 June and 6-8 Aug. Survey dates 1992: 25-27 May, 26-29 June and 26-27 August. The filenames and descriptions are as follows: 1) TRANS91 and TRANS92 survey log with date, total, time, observer, etc 2) TMRLT91 AND TMRLT91 # of murrelets on each transect by survey and group size 3) TOTHER91 AND TOTHER91 # of other species by transect and survey.
